app_name: Groups Control Groups Voice Recording and Karaoke Apps Stingray Karaoke Party
app_description: Start a karaoke party from your phone! With over 20 000 licensed songs to choose from it s easy to start singing. Features Songs in the style of Billie Eilish Lil Nas X Shawn Mendes Queen Bon Jovi and many more All genres: pop rock country Disney show tunes and more A wide range of eras: from yesterday s classics to today s hits A variety of languages Pre made playlists Holiday What s Hot Just In and more Personalized song queues of up to 100 songs Compatibility with Airplay to mirror the karaoke app on Apple TV The option of casting lyrics to TV with Google Chromecast Possibility of singing along to lead lyrics or without them Low bandwidth option by switching the karaoke player to display lyrics on black rather than video Karaoke plans FREE: 5 full length songs updated monthly 9.99: Weekly access for unlimited access to all songs 14.99: Monthly access for unlimited access to all songs Payment will be charged to your iTunes Account at the time of purchase or auto renewal in your local currency equivalent to the USD value as determined by the Apple App Store. You may manage your subscription and turn off the auto renewal by going to your iTunes Account Settings and selecting Subscriptions Sing with Stingray Karaoke View Stingray s Privacy Policy: http: www.stingray.com en privacy policy http: www.stingray.com en terms and conditions Number of songs varies by territory
